comments: Towns (MIN) absorbs the marginal contact initiated by Young (CHI) at the end of the drive.
Towns (MIN) places a stayed hand on Young's (CHI) back side and does not extend or deliver any contact during Young's shot attempt.
At the end of the drive, Towns' (MIN) elbow makes contact with Carter Jr.'s (CHI) face.
Towns (MIN) briefly engages and disengages with Young (CHI) off ball.

Towns (MIN) maintains a legal defensive position alongside LaVine (CHI) and absorbs the marginal contact created by LaVine as he steps towards Towns and finishes his driving shot attempt on the opposite side of the basket.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in White's (CHI) path and does not deliver any contact.
Towns (MIN) legally firms up in Temple's (CHI) path during the pick.
LaVine (CHI) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Beasley (MIN) makes marginal contact with LaVine's (CHI) arm as he completes the pass.
Carter Jr. (CHI) legally contests Towns' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) maintains a legal defensive position on-ball and absorbs the contact as LaVine (CHI) dribbles.
Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact with LaVine's (CHI) arm.
Beasley (MIN) commits a take foul on Satoransky (CHI).
White (CHI) makes contact with Rubio's (MIN) arm during his upward shooting motion.
Okogie (MIN) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
